Method Detail

fieldOpcodeToConstant

public static final byte fieldOpcodeToConstant(int opcode)
Utility method to map a field instruction opcode to its matching Sofya event constant.

Parameters:
opcode - Opcode of the field instruction to be mapped.
Returns:
The Sofya event code that indicates a field event of the type matching the given opcode.
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If the given opcode does not correlate to a field instruction.
